# Plan: Freedom Wall Interaction Feedback & Live Cursors

## Context
The Freedom Wall canvas currently feels static â€” items appear instantly without visual feedback, and there's no sense of other users being present. Two improvements will make it feel alive: a "puff" particle effect when items are placed, and real-time cursor broadcasting so users can see each other moving around the wall.

